FBIS4-67118 "jptdd020__l94103" JPRS-TDD-94-020-L JPRS Narcotics 1 May 1994 WEST EUROPE AUSTRIA Polish Drug Courier Arrested; 2 Kg of Heroin Seized Polish Drug Courier Arrested; 2 Kg of Heroin Seized AU0105144294 Vienna KURIER in German 1 May 94 p 10 AU0105144294 Vienna KURIER German BFN [Unattributed report: "Two Kilos of Heroin Hidden in Broken Down Car"] [Excerpts] The drug trade has to accept the failure of another billion-schilling deal: In a parking lot along the southern highway near Graz, a Pole who had hidden 2 kg of pure heroin with a black-market value of 8 million schillings in his car was arrested. [passage omitted] Andrzej G., 22, from Poland admitted that he was supposed to take the drugs from Poland to Italy. His reward: 1,000 German marks. It is currently investigated whether he had already made "deliveries" along the way before being arrested.
